<L>__{interior train day}
<A>__{seated on a bench is a police matron, and beside her, the boy from the de kalb diner...who we will identify henceforth as "walter." he is looking out the window at the passing scenery.}
<D>__{"walter" did you know that los angeles is where they make the tom mix movies?}
<C>__{matron}
<D>__{no, i didn't. "walter" his horse is named blue.}
<P>__{(beat)}
<D>__{you think they'll let me watch them make a movie?}
<C>__{matron}
<D>__{i don't know, you'll have to ask. but with all this attention, who knows, maybe they will.}
<A>__{the boy turns his attention back out the window as we hear the whistle of the train pulling into union station.}
